cm-cpr-already-being-performed = Кто-то уже проводит СЛР { $target }!
cm-cpr-self-start-perform = Вы начинаете проводить СЛР { $target }!
cm-cpr-other-start-perform = { $performer } начинает проводить СЛР { $target }!
cm-cpr-self-perform = Вы провели СЛР { $target }. Повторяйте по крайней мере каждые { $seconds } секунд.
cm-cpr-other-perform = { $performer } проводит СЛР { $target }.
cm-cpr-self-perform-fail-received-too-recently = Вам не удалось провести СЛР { $target }. Неправильный ритм. Делайте это медленнее.
cm-cpr-other-perform-fail = { $performer } не провести СЛР { $target }!
rmc-cpr-dummy-verb-pickup = Pick up
rmc-cpr-dummy-verb-reset = Reset CPR Counter
rmc-cpr-dummy-deploy-self = You set up the CPR dummy for use.
rmc-cpr-dummy-deploy-others = { $user } sets up a CPR dummy for use!
rmc-cpr-dummy-success-self = You perform CPR on the CPR dummy.
rmc-cpr-dummy-success-others = { $user } performs CPR on a CPR dummy.
rmc-cpr-dummy-fail-self = You fail to perform CPR on the CPR dummy. Incorrect rhythm. Do it slower.
rmc-cpr-dummy-fail-others = { $user } fails to perform CPR on a CPR dummy.
rmc-cpr-dummy-examine-successful = [color=green]Successful CPRs: { $count }.[/color]
rmc-cpr-dummy-examine-failed = [color=red]Failed CPRs: { $count }.[/color]
rmc-cpr-dummy-reset-denied = Resetting the counter is restricted to: { $jobs }
rmc-cpr-dummy-reset-success = You reset the counter on the CPR dummy.
